# This fork repo does not globally ignore bin/ — ignore this project's build output locally.
bin/
obj/

# The per-ABI libmsquic.so is built fresh by CI (.github/workflows/android-publish.yml) and packed
# into the NuGet — it is NOT committed. For a LOCAL pack, build it first with android/build-android.ps1
# (it lands in native/<abi>/ via the csproj RefreshMsQuicNative target).
native/**/*.so
